{"tid":922125,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"抑鬱男持槍自轟臉全毀！經25小時手術「換臉」重生","createTime":"2018-11-30T06:13:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-30T06:48:07.000Z","uid":75969,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"26afe55417854f2b4b1e9c4ebf5dfefe280fe407","tid":922125,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T06:13:04.000Z","msg":"國際中心／綜合報導<br />\n<br />\n美國一名26歲男子昂德伍德（Cameron Underwood），兩年前因為與交往多年的女友分手，再加上諸事不順而罹患了憂鬱症，再一次醉酒後選擇舉槍自轟，昂德伍德雖然保住一命，但臉部幾乎全毀，只剩下前額與眼睛，下半張臉「面目全非」。幸運的是，在經過了醫療評估後，有100位醫療人員替他進行了長達25個小時的手術，現代整形醫學的鬼斧神工讓昂德伍德的臉煥然一新，也終於能正常開口說話了。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2018/11/30/1666293-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2018%2F11%2F30%2F1666293-XXL.jpg&h=b5f2a22b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">▲歷經了25小時的重建手術，昂德伍德獲得新生。（圖／翻攝自鏡報）<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n據英國《鏡報》報導，紐約大學朗格尼醫學中心（NYU Langone Health）為昂德伍德進行了臉部重建手術，100名醫生組成的團隊進行了25個小時的馬拉松手術，藉由3D列印技術重建了臉部模型，再將肌肉、組織與血管連接起來，手術醫師羅卓古茲（Eduardo Rodriguez）表示：「許多人認為這就像戴面具一樣，但沒有那麼簡單，臉部就像拼圖一樣非常棘手，而且我們沒辦法中途放棄。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2018/11/30/1666296-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2018%2F11%2F30%2F1666296-XXL.jpg&h=2d51d53b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">▲手術藉由3D技術重建臉部模型。（圖／翻攝自Nzherald）</span><br />\n<br />\n在手術完成後，昂德伍德也在鏡頭前亮相，不僅重新恢復了型男的模樣，也能正常開口說話，他感謝醫療團隊「再給我一次機會重生」。除此之外，「變臉手術」的幕後還有一位功臣，是23歲的捐贈者威爾（Will Fisher），他在今年1月與精神疾病奮鬥中死亡，然後捐出了心臟、肝臟、腎臟、眼睛和臉，昂德伍德就是其中一名受惠者。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2018/11/30/1666302-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2018%2F11%2F30%2F1666302-XXL.jpg&h=34cd05da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong>▲昂德伍德原來的模樣（左）與捐贈者威爾（右）。（圖／翻攝自Nzherald）</strong><br />\n<br />\n對於威爾的母親而言，兒子的死是一場悲劇，而昂德伍德的存在能幫助她度過悲傷的情緒，她曾告訴記者：「我很開心威爾能幫助昂德伍德擁有更好的人生。」（編輯：周羿彣）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=464071\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D464071&d=XJlrGENh4tChnQbLgu56%2FTANphTrK3OAdhrcB0lChBw%3D&h=916ebd98\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D464071&h=cedde705\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=464071</a>"},{"pid":"e56f27b5112408e833ff137ee04e9ec87782dc6f","tid":922125,"uid":169364,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T06:21:38.000Z","msg":"咁都唔死<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf1f3f58cccf8515bf26c2ed81e8c058d78ecd07","tid":922125,"uid":17359,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T06:22:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yZTU1JR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyZTU1JR.png&h=b2d525a5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b29917d251911bddcd086ae97733d6f79abacb78","tid":922125,"uid":22694,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"cf1f3f58cccf8515bf26c2ed81e8c058d78ecd07","tid":922125,"uid":17359,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T06:22:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yZTU1JR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyZTU1JR.png&h=b2d525a5&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T06:24:04.000Z","msg":"如眼睛可分對或錯~"},{"pid":"0af0b755d1ed89d9c68bb397476d4a695312d7f1","tid":922125,"uid":10056,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T06:26:01.000Z","msg":"又要自殺又要人救 真係攞黎搞 你話不幸有意外就話姐"},{"pid":"275ea9a63d8ce4b42b7994681c8a2df02ff32779","tid":922125,"uid":1467,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T06:28:21.000Z","msg":"依啲就高清大圖⋯⋯"},{"pid":"a168c393030fc8e5fa406e63e5bca289ce02a900","tid":922125,"uid":11148,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy